        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Toggle"><image src="wo_collapse.png" align="left" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Toggle"></image><toggle type="dropdown" print-expanded="true" help-expanded="false" defaultstyle="false" translate="true" src-collapsed="wo_collapse.png" src-expanded="wo_expanded.png" src-print="wo_toggle_print.png" styleclass="Toggle"><caption translate="true"><![CDATA[Value Mapping]]></caption></toggle></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="Table_Toggle" rowcount="1" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:5px; border-top:none; border-right:none; border-bottom:none;">
        </td>
        <td style="width:970px; border:none;">
          <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">This demo is based on Water Office. See also the video on </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="weblink" href="https://cavdb186.home.xs4all.nl/mapmarkers/index.html" target="_blank" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">the website</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="TableText"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="17" colcount="3" style="width:100%; cell-padding:2px; cell-spacing:1px;">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"></para>
              </td>
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">1.</text></para>
              </td>
              <td>
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">Create and run a query for all </text><text styleclass="TableText" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Measurement Points;</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"></para>
              </td>
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">2.</text></para>
              </td>
              <td>
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">Select the records in the result of the Explorer and Click </text><text styleclass="TableText" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Goto</text><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">;</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"></para>
              </td>
              <td style="vertical-align:top; width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Result sign" translate="true">»</text></para>
              </td>
              <td>
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">If there is no Generic or specific Mapping, the points are show with the default symbol and default text;</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"></para>
              </td>
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">3.</text></para>
              </td>
              <td>
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">If one or more records are not displayed, check View Defaults Goto size and raise its value;</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"></para>
              </td>
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">4.</text></para>
              </td>
              <td>
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">Open the Configuration GUI</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"></para>
              </td>
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">5. </text></para>
              </td>
              <td>
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">Select the Symbol Definition &quot;Bar-BlueRed&quot; and Click </text><text styleclass="TableText" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Create Symbol</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"></para>
              </td>
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">6.</text></para>
              </td>
              <td>
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">Select the realised Symbol &quot;Bar-BlueRed&quot;</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"></para>
              </td>
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">7.</text></para>
              </td>
              <td>
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">Open the tab </text><text styleclass="TableText" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Goto Mappings</text><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true"> and select in the mapping tree </text><text styleclass="TableText" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Specific</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"></para>
              </td>
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">8.</text></para>
              </td>
              <td>
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">Select in the </text><text styleclass="TableText" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Rwo Hierarchy List</text><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true"> the object Measurement Point</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"></para>
              </td>
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">9.</text></para>
              </td>
              <td>
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">Click the button </text><text styleclass="TableText" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Set</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"></para>
              </td>
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">10.</text></para>
              </td>
              <td>
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">Refresh the map</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"></para>
              </td>
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Result sign" translate="true">»</text></para>
              </td>
              <td>
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">Measurement points are now drawn with a bar graph.</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"></para>
              </td>
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"></para>
              </td>
              <td>
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">We now are going to change the properties of the symbol;</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"></para>
              </td>
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">11.</text></para>
              </td>
              <td>
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">Select in the Configuration Gui the realised Symbol &quot;Bar-BlueRed&quot; and the tab </text><text styleclass="TableText" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Symbol Properties</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"></para>
              </td>
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">12.</text></para>
              </td>
              <td>
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">Add a value_selector</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"></para>
              </td>
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">13.</text></para>
              </td>
              <td>
                <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">Define (optional) a value scale.</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="width:20px;">
                <para styleclass="TableText"></para>
              </td>
              <td style="width:20px;">
